  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>冯雨晨</span> <span>2026-03-09 17:09</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p>以下文章来源于：投资界</p>\n  <strong>投资界</strong>\n  <p>清科控股旗下创业与投资资讯平台</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d5f224ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeF3icnattSiciavmvLy3hCTRLJMa1xlXicYiafFkDqz2zusB0BarOpic3o7LSFQMY8WPpLVCPFlHfH8J2eyH90WogP4mBCtRVrqtAicdU%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"height: 308px;width: 578px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/o02wSnKAPeHQicdUgCk7icb7sqWb0y8B5bOFIQfT25ewsQGYBtnwibI1lkTLA40ZRde7H58SiburKqV7uo9RjhdBj5w3zzac1Pgql4eaSxO6D2Y/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"308\" data-imgfileid=\"101396983\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=784d1960&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fo02wSnKAPeHQicdUgCk7icb7sqWb0y8B5bOFIQfT25ewsQGYBtnwibI1lkTLA40ZRde7H58SiburKqV7uo9RjhdBj5w3zzac1Pgql4eaSxO6D2Y%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"39\" data-imgfileid=\"101298595\" data-ratio=\"0.06666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"height: 39px;width: 578px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d8a30ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0Lereibp3GVwr7pAWURUC5MH7xdLsTMSsaiayEzicByDcKTBHnpsGXGoTVQQ5Iyw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI魔幻时代。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"101298596\" data-ratio=\"0.08888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"900\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d266c885&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQDFNHs0vUhrvC75JRXlG0rM2iat53EoZMsodUxkMSYWXNSIFUEeuo2I89A9ibZcCic1oNlHEWLAxeWpFZgeic0wdtg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.024074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: 14px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"25\" data-imgfileid=\"101298593\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aedec240&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibplkrJOvk6R1Efiaq0NlWibAtLj0DDlMWGggbQ9KdrLibUvZbz91W4FNd7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">文</span></span></strong><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">冯雨晨</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源｜</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">投资界（ID：pedaily2012）</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">封面来源</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenClaw官网</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">别惊讶，你隔壁工位的同事正在变成一群龙虾。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">“肇事者”是一位奥地利退休程序员。在财务自由后岁月静好的日子里，他发现市场上还没有一款AI可以通过发消息帮自己处理事情，闲暇之余，他手搓了一个AI助手推上了GitHub。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">于是，一只叫做OpenClaw的红色大龙虾刷爆全网。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">它是这么干活的</span>：你先授予这只龙虾电脑的完全操作权限，好好“养”它，让它了解你的偏好、行为、工作以及拓展学习。然后，这只龙虾就将成为你的数字分身——替你读新闻、发邮件、写代码、发租房帖，甚至替你花钱和赚钱。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">这一次，AI不是在辅助你，而是替你行动。“演进的剧烈程度超乎想象”，面对龙虾冲击，投资人们不吝直言。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 40px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">往往不经意间，一个崭新的未来就来了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101296245\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6f13e36e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vYs92nHCpdbueQF7gdhICh6n4bg74ZZBRll6JriaDqWuAUKCORW2pdPf2yVUIWtCJ5r1TYvaDtK5CA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 52, 198);font-weight: bold;\">养龙虾爆红</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 52, 198);font-weight: bold;\">Kimi、MiniMax流量暴涨</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">有两个水生小动物让AI圈深深着迷：一头蓝色鲸鱼，一只红色龙虾。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">以蓝色鲸鱼为标识的DeepSeek，</span>曾掀起算力平权狂潮，把原本昂贵的高阶推理能力打成了白菜价，让每个人都能拥有免费且强大的数字军师。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">画着红色小龙虾Logo的OpenClaw则带来另一种颠覆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">它是一个拥有电脑底层权限的数字执行者，通过“养虾人”的私有数据喂养后，只需丢出一句指令，这只龙虾就能接管你的鼠标和键盘，跨越各种APP围墙，替你把事情办了。甚至，它能够去产生实际商业动作，替你支付，替你赚钱。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101396982\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=de0e2a7e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fo02wSnKAPeFGMT2vAByvbI0bdZhg8qegWB6K4BoRdIBzCxcwdrYOKkcjzvicBs92Q5M131ZCO8yB51mLibGESZyLL4DjDkdvA0eIz6wdfunoc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">“人类终于等来了数字牛马”，这无疑令人兴奋。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">OpenClaw有多火？诞生几周内它就席卷了GitHub，成为历史上增长最快的开源项目，作为能够高效运行OpenClaw的苹果主机Mac mini直接因此销量暴涨。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">大模型厂商们则更兴奋——谁能和OpenClaw深度适配，谁就能成为全球流量入口。尤其在中国赛场，月之暗面、Minimax纷纷上线了可快速使用OpenClaw相关功能的Kimi Claw、MaxClaw，智谱则推出可云端运行的AutoGLM-OpenClaw。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">于是我们看到，OpenClaw爆火期间，中国模型厂商平台调用量挤进全球前列。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">当然，这把火也烧到了爱看项目的投资圈。“这么热，必须研究”，投资界了解到，不仅是投AI的，投具身机器人的、生命科技的投资人们都在研究如何养虾，还有投资人公开发贴：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">“求一位能帮我养龙虾的人。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">放眼望去，养龙虾产业链悄然成型。OpenClaw的安装对普通用户来说不算简单，因此从几百元到上万元，OpenClaw已经催生出了上门收费安装服务。就在今天，大厂下场开卷，腾讯官方宣布：不要998，不要448，今天鹅厂门口现场免费安装OpenClaw。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">“大家都在养龙虾，不参与让我焦虑”，一位朋友如是坦言。还有法律界人士聊起：以前圈里人对许多AI工具兴趣都不是那么高，但OpenClaw火了之后，法律圈里开始有一批人自发尝试。猎豹移动董事长傅盛也高调为OpenClaw站台，称14天成功养出7*24小时自动运转的超级AI团队。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 48px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">无论你准没准备好、答不答应，AI风暴，来到了全民养虾时代。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101296246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=42f04bbb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vYs92nHCpdbueQF7gdhICh6MebCYnvZdvTDPbOUA7ibvzc0o3YBuC9FURHiaKksE5qUFLohPK7nDqRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 52, 198);font-weight: bold;\">一位财务自由工程师</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 52, 198);font-weight: bold;\">魔幻漂流</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">追溯起来，OpenClaw的诞生充满了个人英雄主义色彩。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">身后创始人Peter Steinberger在Github上的个人简介如此写道：Came back from retirement to mess with AI. Previously: Founder of @PSPDFKit.</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">相信你也感受到了，这是一个功成身退的创业者为AI重返游乐场的故事。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"101396981\" data-ratio=\"0.5268518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e6422d67&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fo02wSnKAPeHMQ496BSKJs6GTXdAVvasPnLPpfd142UNvv9WndMrvKPlrBnVMytxjFpsFNyiatDD2WkwicC7J3C286ibpbst45TicefPE9ZFPxiac%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">图注：OpenClaw创始人Peter Steinberger</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">Steinberger来自奥地利小镇，少年时期就萌生出对编程的超凡兴趣，后来考入维也纳科技大学计算机专业。自然而然地，他毕业后选择去硅谷初创公司闯荡。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">彼时，第一代iPad发布不久，Steinberge觉得用iPad看PDF不顺眼，于是自己动手做了一个PDF的集成工具。就这样，赶上电子化浪潮，他辞职创立了PSPDFkit。这次创业是成功的，PSPDFkit吸纳了Apple、IBM、大众汽车等一众知名客户。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">“那几年我一直高速运转，经营公司很辛苦”，Steinberger曾如此回忆这次创业。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">2021年，他急流勇退——以1亿欧元的价格将经营十多年的PSPDFKit多数股权出售。在大众眼中，这位工程师无疑已经财富自由。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">不过恐怕连他自己也没想到，几年后，流淌的编程血液还将唤醒一场更大的盛宴。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">2025年，优秀的开源AI大模型逐渐走向成熟，一批代码生成工具开始内测。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">恰逢其时，对AI应用创业者们，这是一个条件已经极其丰裕的时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">Steinberger也玩AI。他内心萌生了一个原始诉求：能不能通过WhatsApp跟电脑互动，让AI帮我办事？熟悉的一幕再次上演。他又自己动手搞了一个AI助手，先在WhatsApp接收消息，接着调用终端AI编程助手Claude Code，然后返回结果。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">一个人，一小时手搓，搞定。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">于是，这样一个Agent诞生了：</span>给这个Agent提供工具和完全的电脑访问权限，它可以自己想出解决方案，即使你根本没编程过。经过更新优化后，2025年11月底，崇尚开源的Steinberger在Github正式上线了这个项目：Clawdbot（改名后为OpenClaw）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 48px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">爆炸性时刻到来。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"101296247\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c1ff179&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vYs92nHCpdbueQF7gdhICh69wicwdn3toUy1ib4ibVYZAHQXc4c9XqWjVkuIuz4WTgftXHEwpbIRia8KA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 52, 198);font-weight: bold;\">“AI海啸才刚刚开始”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">狂欢之际，一场关乎生产力重构的想象正在上演。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">一位投资人朋友在使用OpenClaw一个月后感慨：“我更加确定这场AI海啸才刚刚开始。这次的烈度，保守估计是移动互联网的五倍，商业层面可能是十倍以上。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">这并不难理解。过去许多年来，跑通一个商业闭环要先有融资，再经过漫长招聘雇佣合适的团队，还要持续支付不菲的运营成本。但在OpenClaw这类Agent的颠覆下，有了一批不知疲倦的数字打工人，可以全天候处理数据、运营内容，甚至操控实体设备。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">换言之，一个人加上几台电脑，就是一支数字牛马满编的商业舰队。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">但当人人都可以是一支商业舰队的时候，未来竞争和投资逻辑将如何变革？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">对于那些过去以APP孤岛抢占用户注意力的古典互联网巨头，旧秩序的考验也摆在眼前：当Agent和Agent直接沟通、人和Agent之间交互，传统流量入口下的商业模式是否还行之有效？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">新世界风暴到来之前，隐患暗流同样汹涌。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">用户在兴奋地交出鼠标和键盘控制权的同时，也在交出数字世界的底牌——OpenClaw需要访问邮箱、日历、系统命令等核心权限，顶级投资机构Institutional Investor近日就明确提到：OpenClaw展示了AI Agent的能力，但安全漏洞致命、治理框架空白、不可预测性是常态。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">但无论如何，潘多拉魔盒已然打开。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">OpenClaw现象预演了一个信号：AI正从对话走向执行，我们来到了大模型脑力平权与智能体行动力平权的交汇时刻。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 48px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 15px;\">大门已经被徐徐推开，在门后等待着我们的，也许不仅是一场生产力解放，还将是人类商业史上一次残酷的优胜劣汰。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.06666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: 39px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"51\" data-imgfileid=\"101298594\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd023431&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibpOTKhlQucdMlnua1EZPEftBTh3iaNT7QPQlFYa6jHJ58VcEIpc2SXg7A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.06666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);height: 39px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"51\" data-imgfileid=\"101298598\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=62a9ba52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibpaO1bAicFfUgxRicmVz0WLEJINuCCErEc1KS2r8fuFZCicO3END8ibSE2Ng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDk5NzA0Mw==&amp;mid=2248880227&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b8022b0f9089612424641c01689b952f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/o02wSnKAPeEKto5St0TSrQRQtib66TNyBYicTaGsguMcvuia42OnIeI8X24ZQsiaxIF4DZK3sHqcTqwlbXFVffibkCsIVKxibM8wEmM5oblibibGyyM/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;